  <section>
    <h2>How To Build Dual Statements</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Start with standard IFRS/GAAP accounts.</li>
      <li>Deduct the calculated <strong>User Cost</strong> after net income.</li>
      <li>Restate investment returns using <strong>SWACC</strong> instead of classic WACC or discount rates.</li>
      <li>Disclose all green/social CapEx, carbon, and human capital investments explicitly.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>
