      <li><strong>Accountability:</strong> Investors and citizens can see if rents are truly future-proofed, not consumed.</li>
      <li><strong>Policy Implications:</strong> Supports sustainable tax policy, royalty design, and resource management.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      <strong>Novelty:</strong> This dual reporting system is one of the first of its kind, offering a rigorous, actionable framework for sustainable resource accounting.
